{"tid":354840,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手同另一半講你未玩夠嘅入一入黎","createTime":"2017-08-10T19:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T03:51:17.000Z","uid":121316,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"761452decb5434eb7f756533d1e6c73b1f48f982","tid":354840,"uid":121316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:31:26.000Z","msg":"你到底有無諗過，你講呢句嘢係幾不負責任；<br />\n你到底有無諗過，佢真係有決心同你定落黎？<br />\n<br />\n你到底記唔記得，點解當初你地兩個會一齊；<br />\n你到底記唔記得，你地一齊果陣有幾咁開心？<br />\n<br />\n你到底知唔知道，你講出口果一刻佢嘅心情；<br />\n你到底知唔知道，佢愛你但亦只能選擇離開？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f33cdffc7d58ea5feaaa795e814ec4dfbe5e0d6","tid":354840,"uid":4998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:36:27.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<br />\n只可以講他朝君體也相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0e9e3d817b1c14e1ecb81310f5f5acc5904eaf","tid":354840,"uid":4998,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I know that feel<br />\n只可以講他朝君體也相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n祝條仆街可以玩<br />\n玩得開心啲<br />\n玩到出事<br />\n玩到有一日會做返我既角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過老老豆豆講句 <br />\n未玩夠只係藉口<br />\n只係唔愛你"},{"pid":"578e0ef62ff24a06c778c424b46846d48f3bee73","tid":354840,"uid":121316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>I know that feel<br />\n只可以講他朝君體也相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n祝條仆街可以玩<br />\n玩得開心啲<br />\n玩到出事<br />\n玩到有一日會做返我既角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過老老豆豆講句 <br />\n未玩夠只係藉口<br />\n只係唔愛你</blockquote><br />\n問題係佢真係出咗去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59630aa6fa9f435f9acc3f7d8382b4b693ed2445","tid":354840,"uid":109263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T21:07:58.000Z","msg":"仲有句「我真係愛你架，但朋友比戀人重要」<br />\n果時我真係比佢吹到啤一聲"},{"pid":"6f2c5cdb4ea36921775fc2e3cdc89412b90eebaa","tid":354840,"uid":121316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有句「我真係愛你架，但朋友比戀人重要」<br />\n果時我真係比佢吹到啤一聲</blockquote><br />\n所以話都唔明有啲人點解要玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d41cc264c05fb27bf5d780a5ee0ca13df450c78","tid":354840,"uid":81683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩夠未"},{"pid":"5da1bb9c18ba6c70b147f93a70536b9779a1620b","tid":354840,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:55:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞</span></span>"},{"pid":"ff8aa272bda5d55398613c710608e5880875d5b1","tid":354840,"uid":121316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩夠未</blockquote><br />\n「其實我未玩夠，分手啦。」"},{"pid":"0d1f91ad971fbaa0c80264675289c3c41de3e4c9","tid":354840,"uid":121316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">雞 全部都係雞</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a76548b4c558b28e5ea0a8538f715c20a411ce6","tid":354840,"uid":24854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:48:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b6feadecb6a1167e783bfcd39d1a5105ff249f8","tid":354840,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩夠未</blockquote><br />\n「其實我未玩夠，分手啦。」</blockquote><br />\n咩未玩夠姐<br />\n其實我唔愛你炸<br />\n醒下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ead18684ef830dc699a731cca74019ac032587f","tid":354840,"uid":61195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中"},{"pid":"95a29440a0f1f27fd3a8b5cd97276a51abbcf6ea","tid":354840,"uid":24854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T15:59:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"baaa3240d8d3a774d80f51e44388ded4a326032a","tid":354840,"uid":109385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"我知啊<br />\n但我係要講啊<br />\n吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ef8106d69b08d6c44d30ad0073d9d1bd65bb52","tid":354840,"uid":24542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e867afebc8811306d7089165da26511b02f9618","tid":354840,"uid":20967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"好垃圾依句野"},{"pid":"2f620c96e2004205d2f2526a5f77beaabf67188a","tid":354840,"uid":37427,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"曾經有條女俾左幾次帽我都原諒佢<br />\n最後見佢死性不改就主動同佢散左<br />\n前年佢搵番我，咁大家當普通朋友傾計<br />\n點知條女話同我散完之後無一條仔對佢好<br />\n話原來最好果個係我<br />\n重要仔都落過一次<br />\n跟住自己玩夠啦，易家無出去玩了專心事業（做sales)<br />\n之後講野係咁想當年，暗示想我埋佢單咁<br />\nSorry啦，我就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我邊有咁既資格<br />\n當初晚晚出去飲酒食仔真係唔明點解頂得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n易家心都涼哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以各位俾臭雞飛既巴打唔洗灰<br />\n改變自己重新出發，到時件臭雞見你人又好又搵到錢，就自然會搵番你，不過要唔要一齊番就自己決定啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a16218471c39781437962324c70882c8664d3b","tid":354840,"uid":163800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"要玩吾該搵player同你玩個夠，player吾會同你認真，易黎易去，你玩啲對感情認真嘅女仔真係好不負責任。你只係想得到個女仔，但人地可能真心想同你發展，到頭黎你玩夠就同人分手你有無唸過人地感受？？？？追人個陣就講到自己有幾鍾意人，甚至塑造自己成為一個穩重男人咁，係傻豬先會信你係好男人。追到手之後就話自己吾成熟，比吾到未來你，仲想去追其他女仔，同你分開係為你好。真係多謝哂！！！雖然你曾經比人hurt過，但係你報復係其他女仔身上實在可悲！每個人都值得被愛，你都吾例外。人地吾愛你，請你都要好好愛你自己，日後總有人會願意去愛惜你。玩感情其實係糟側人地同時糟側緊自己，你根本得吾到愛，因為你從來都無打開過你個心去接受人地嘅愛，更無愛過人。請你吾好再害人啦，一啲都吾好玩，你亦吾會得到別人嘅尊重同愛，你個心永遠都係咁空虛。呢個世界除左感情，仲有好多野可以玩，好自為之啦你。"}]}